Package: libmaus0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: data structures and algorithms for bioinformatics
 libmaus contains:
 .
  - I/O classes (single byte and UTF-8)
  - bitio classes (input, output and various forms of bit level manipulation)
  - text indexing classes (suffix and LCP array, fulltext and minute (FM), ...)
  - BAM sequence alignment files input/output (simple and collating)

Package: libmaus-dev
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libdevel
Depends: libmaus0 (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for libmaus.
 Libmaus is a collection of data structures and algorithms for bioinformatics.

